---

<section class="px-6 py-20 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4">
    First-class AI integration
  </h2>
  <p class="text-text-secondary text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    Pyrite speaks MCP natively. Connect Claude Desktop, Claude Code, Cursor, or
    any MCP-compatible AI — your knowledge base becomes persistent agent memory.
  </p>

  <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
    <div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Three-tier access control</h3>
      <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span
            class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 shrink-0"
            >read</span
          >
          <span class="text-text-secondary"
            >Search, browse, explore — 14 tools. Safe for untrusted agents.</span
          >
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span
            class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 shrink-0"
            >write</span
          >
          <span class="text-text-secondary"
            >Create, update, delete, link entries — +6 tools. For your own
            agents.</span
          >
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span
            class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono bg-red-500/10 text-red-400 shrink-0"
            >admin</span
          >
          <span class="text-text-secondary"
            >Index management, git operations — +4 tools. For you.</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Connect in seconds</h3>
      <div
        class="bg-surface-overlay rounded-lg p-4 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed"
      >
        <p class="text-text-muted">// claude_desktop_config.json</p>
        <p>{"{"}</p>
        <p class="pl-4">"mcpServers": {"{"}</p>
        <p class="pl-8">"pyrite": {"{"}</p>
        <p class="pl-12">
          "command": "<span class="text-pyrite-400">pyrite</span>",
        </p>
        <p class="pl-12">"args": ["<span class="text-pyrite-400">mcp</span>"]</p>
        <p class="pl-8">{"}"}</p>
        <p class="pl-4">{"}"}</p>
        <p>{"}"}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
